<section id="main" class="h-[92vh] bg-[url('/layered-steps-haikei.svg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-repeat-x" >
  <div class="container mx-auto w-5/6 md:w-2/3  pt-10 sm:pt-12 md:pt-16 lg:pt-20 xl:pt-28">
    <h1 class="text-center text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
      <span>Simplify yours links</span>
    </h1>
    <h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
      Share and grab your visitors
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center max-w-lg mt-3 text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 block md:mt-5 mx-auto">This app can short your links and grab data about your visitors. Try it inserting your link in the next field, copy the short link and share it wherever you want!
    </p>

    <%= form_with url: "/" do |form| %>
    <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 flex justify-center">
      <div class="shadow-md">
        <input name="url" class="focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 focus:outline-none appearance-none w-ful md:px-10l text-sm leading-6 text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400 rounded-md py-2 pl-10 ring-1 ring-slate-200 shadow-sm md:py-3 md:text-lg"
          type="text" placeholder="Write a url here.">
      </div>
      <div class="ml-1 sm:ml-3 rounded-md shadow-md">
        <input name="commit" type="submit" value="shorten" class="w-full px-6 md:px-8  py-2 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 md:py-3 md:text-lg">
      </div>
    </div>
    <% end %>

    <turbo-frame id="flash">
      <%= render 'shared/flash' %>
    </turbo-frame>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="aboutit" class="">
    <div class="container mx-auto w-5/6 md:w-2/3  pt-10 sm:pt-12 md:pt-16 lg:pt-20 xl:pt-28 flex flex-wrap">
      <h2 class="mx-auto text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl pb-10 sm:pb-12 md:pb-16 lg:pb-20 xl:pb-28">
        About the project
      </h2>
      <dl class="mx-auto">
        <dt class="mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold"> What is this? </h3>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mb-16 mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl
lg:mx-0">
          <p> Paso is a URL Shortener with advanced analytics for the traffic through your links, visitors on your blog, forum or website. This is build using the <a href="https://github.com/a-chacon/rails_url_shortener"
              target="_blank">RailsUrlShortener</a> engine. </p>
        </dd> <dt class="mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold"> Features </h3>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mb-16 mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0">
          <p>
            For now we can log the next information about the visits on your link:
          <ul class="list-disc pt-1">
            <li class="">Ip and related information like: geolocation, ISP.</li>
            <li class="">User Agent and related information: Browser, OS, is a bot.</li>
          </ul>
          </p>
        </dd> <dt class="mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold"> Support this project. </h3>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mb-16 mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0">
          <p> This is an experimental project and
            will be running on free servers, so it will be limited. You can build your own Url Shortener or Ip logger using the RailsUrlShortener engine and help to build new features for that library or for this project. If you like, at least give
            it a start.
          </p>
        </dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
</section>
